8bit RPG
============
Hello everyone! This my university project for the course 'Programing with Python' In the following days the game will be under heavy development so stay tuned.

Legal Notice
============
All 8-bit images (<(100x100px)) are property of Zeboyd Games. This game is created with the CC agreement and is strictly non-comercial.

Running the program
============
The game has an executable in the 'build' directory (RPG-main.exe). You can run it from there.
If you want to run it from the Python IDLE, just open RPG-main.py and execute it.
